metadata.name: Poopsie #2
metadata.description: Who are Pixie + Poopsie? These BFFs represent everyday life. One day is glittery unicorn rainbows, and the next is a total Poop show! Life is all about balance and harmony - good/bad, ups/downs, happy/crappy. They’re here to bridge Web2 and Web3 by building community PODs - People, Opportunity & Dreams. Pixie and Poopsie’s hometown is a little place we like to call Poo-ville! Where the grass is greener where you fertilize it and the rainbows end in unicorns! A place where our friends work to harmonize the hustle culture and create communities focused providing resources for health, wellness and mindset with a huge helping of giggles, shenanigans and lots of chocolate and cheesecake!
